PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of GERARD J. FITZPATRICK of York, Prince Edward Island, as a member of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Blanche M. Keats, whose term has expired.
